parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded. The knocking/tapping noise can also lead to engine failure, causing damage to the engine and potentially leading to a fire.
symptoms: The engine makes a loud knocking or tapping noise
the engine stalls
the check engine light illuminates
the oil pressure warning indicator illuminates
and the vehicle may vibrate or shake.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch master cylinder can cause the clutch pedal to stick to the floor, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
and the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Fire Risk Due to Fuse Issue
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuse can cause a fire, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle may catch on fire due to a faulty fuse
and the driver may experience a burning smell or see smoke.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities, compromising the safety of the driver and passengers.
symptoms: Airbag warning light illuminates
airbags fail to deploy in a crash
seatbelts fail to lock or retract
loud clunking noise from the rear buckle assembly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of seatbelts to lock or retract can lead to serious injuries or fatalities, compromising the safety of the driver and passengers.
symptoms: Seatbelts fail to lock or retract
loud clunking noise from the rear buckle assembly
seatbelts become unbuckled while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of airbag sensors can lead to false warnings, failure of airbags to deploy, or unintended deployment of airbags, compromising the safety of the driver and passengers.
symptoms: Airbag warning light illuminates
airbag sensor malfunction
unintended deployment of airbags.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of dealerships to properly repair recalled vehicles can lead to continued safety risks for drivers and passengers.
symptoms: Dealerships fail to diagnose or repair recalled vehicles
parts are unavailable
repairs are incomplete or inadequate.
